@startuml
title Athena JS CLI bootstrap (before hardening)

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam Rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #FFF4CC
  BorderColor #C28B00
}
skinparam ArrowColor #7A7A7A

actor "Developer" as Dev

rectangle "bin/athena-js.js" as Bin #FFD966
rectangle "dist/cli/index.js" as CliDist #B7DEE8
rectangle "Node ESM Loader" as Loader #F4B183
rectangle "Terminal Output" as Output #F8CECC

Dev --> Bin : run `athena-js`
Bin --> CliDist : dynamic import('../dist/cli/index.js')
Bin --> Loader : resolve module
Loader --> Output : ERR_MODULE_NOT_FOUND\n(raw stack trace)

note right of Output
No pre-check for missing generated CLI bundle.
Failure is cryptic for global installs.
end note

@enduml
